in mainline: tag with the release number: "bzr tag 2.1.1"

on the server: branch trunk to a release-branch with "bzr branch trunk
    bionet-2.1.1"

check out the release branch

in the branch: ./autogen.sh

in the branch: export VERSION=$(grep BIONET_RELEASE_VERSION common.am | cut -d '=' -f 2) ; cd .. ; tar --exclude .bzr -cjf bionet-$VERSION.tar.bz2 bionet-$VERSION

build the docs, install on our webserver

send out an announcement email with links to the tarball and the API docs,
and the top of the changelog

